The paper discusses approaches for retrieving paragraphs to populate a Wikipedia article, which involves information retrieval, natural language processing, and machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.IR (Information Retrieval), followed by cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.DL (Deep Learning).
